snippet.title: "I'm Screwed" Amber Heard Loses Critical Advantage In Lawsuit!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Lost A Critical Advantage In Her Lawsuit! Johnny Depp Is Bringing It Back!

✅ SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCiKzneRB4I4eTN_bHEqV-gg?sub_confirmation=1

The big deal at the moment is that Heard has just failed to have a case dropped against her, which Johnny Depp called for, giving her a big loss. This lawsuit, of course, is the one trying to expose her earlier claims of donating money to charity, the money coming from one of the older lawsuits with Depp. The claim in question being, whether she has donated every penny yet, or is purposely delaying donating for financial gain.

#AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp
